ğŸ” What the Scanner Checks
1. Security Headers

âœ… Strict-Transport-Security (HSTS)

âœ… Content-Security-Policy (CSP)

âœ… X-Content-Type-Options

âœ… X-Frame-Options

âœ… X-XSS-Protection

